profile: JRE Hardware manufactures architectural & glazing hardware in high-quality stainless steel.  Product lines include; railing system components, curtain wall & glass canopy hardware, commercial accessibility grab bars, door hardware (door pulls, sliding doors, barn door systems, pivot & patch fitting), wall mounted wine pegs, as well as toilet & bath finishing accessories.  Our products are distributed using retail and wholesale platforms, project based through General Contractors and homeowners, as well as through competitive project tenders for multifamily and care facility construction projects.
